The Inspector-General of Police, Mohammed Adamu, has ordered the redeployment of the Commissioner of Police in Rivers State, Dandaura Mustapha. Adamu’s directive was disclosed by the Force Public Relations Officer, Frank Mba, on Friday evening. According to a statement by Mba, Mustapha is now replaced with Joseph Gobum Mukari. Mba stated that the redeployment takes immediate effect. Details later…